entries.s_f1bd17f2: Sir! I am ready for my assignment, sir!
entries.s_dcd8623e: Sir! I would like to donate to the war effort. My last act as a civilian... sir.
entries.s_daffa30b: Oh really? Why don't you just back off!
entries.s_c460e647: Outstanding! What equipment will you need?
entries.s_ac02bc4c: Look! Get out of here, now.
entries.s_a095b54f: Actually, I have some business to attend to before I can sign in.
entries.s_9e3acb05: Outstanding, Pilot! How much will you donate to your Empire?
entries.s_919e66c4: I see. What sort of ship do you think you'll need, then?
entries.s_9177e268: I advise you to make it fast, Pilot. The war waits for no one.
entries.s_8d16305a: Sorry, sir! I apologize. I'm just nervous.
entries.s_7e996dfd: That's it! I don't want to see you here again! Get back on the shuttle and get off of this base or I will call the MP's and have you tossed out of an airlock!
entries.s_7bb9cd35: Hm. That's interesting... This is a military recruiting station, my friend! You don't get here by mistake!
entries.s_77d62be0: Sir! I am ready for my ship assignment, sir!
entries.s_6e8fe246: Threatening me, eh? You'd get out of here if you knew what was good for you!
entries.s_6b65d95: What can I do for you, pilot?
entries.s_5f1e2428: I swear - I didn't mean to come here. In fact, can you direct me to a transport? I really must be going, now.
entries.s_5e865634: Done. Here's your starship keycard. Good luck.
entries.s_578cba1: This is wartime, Pilot. Put your emotions aside. Now, are you ready to sign in?
entries.s_4c76a3f0: I'm sorry, but I cannot help you. There is no civilian business aboard the space station. I'd advise you to leave, my friend.
entries.s_31fc03a8: Sorry, I think I'm in the wrong place.
entries.s_14aaf93d: Are you ready to take command of your Star Destroyer, now?
